Package gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc

Enum DegreeFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DegreeFormat>
      • gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc.DegreeFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DegreeFormat>
    public enum DegreeFormat
extends java.lang.Enum<DegreeFormat>
    This class represents the degree formats supported by SSC.

    Note: The integer values for this enumeration cannot be arbitrarily assigned. They must match the values expected by other parts of the SSC software.

    Version:
    $Revison: $
    Author:
    B. Harris
